{"tid":1891082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】武漢將再建19間「方艙醫院」","createTime":"2020-02-21T14:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T10:51:58.000Z","uid":49643,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"53ce9f5b99637fc63a63a74721b1a193b1c2ef15","tid":1891082,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:32:14.000Z","msg":"內地新型冠狀病毒疫情嚴峻，武漢市常務副市長胡亞波在湖北省防疫工作發布會上表示，武漢計劃再建設19家專收輕症患者的「方艙醫院」，預計到本月25日，武漢市儲備的方艙醫院牀位將達3萬張。<br />\n<br />\n胡亞波表示，除增加牀位，也要加強方艙醫院的醫療設備配置，確保每一家方艙醫院都可為患者作電腦掃描（CT），亦要進一步提升供氧能力，並增加心電監測儀等設施設備，以提高方艙醫院救治病人的能力。<br />\n<br />\n目前，武漢已經有13家方艙醫院啟用，提供共13,348張救治牀位，其中9313張已使用；全國各地有72隊支援武漢的醫療隊進入方艙醫院工作。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20200221/s00004/1582292614514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20200221%2Fs00004%2F1582292614514&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=a40f52b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20200221%2Fs00004%2F1582292614514&h=44210f7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20200221/s00004/1582292614514</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe597f0c24ac18e4357a1f7a58f990e1734e9601","tid":1891082,"uid":20170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"冇人病嘅話，點解要起咁多醫生"},{"pid":"9d818fce2896337cd189cc27846eadc937a6b989","tid":1891082,"uid":331421,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"疫情放緩唔係要關閉醫院先係既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca904e39c495353df97699a7d556975cda7047ee","tid":1891082,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:34:20.000Z","msg":"沒事沒事<br 